text: Novoshakhovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Vosmomartovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 262 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Yermekeyevo, 15 km from Selo imeni 8 Marta. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Novoshakhovo
